---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: English Home
description: English entry point for the research workflow guidebook.
lang: en
activeSection: home
langSwitch:
  url: /ko/
  label: 한국어
pageClass: page-home
---
<main>
  <section class="home-hero">
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy-block">
        <p class="eyebrow">English Home</p>
        <h1>From first setup to confident collaboration.</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
          Start with the tools that get a first compile working, move into the everyday writing
          loop, and then stabilize your Git and GitHub workflow for real research projects.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/en/start-here/">Begin with Start Here</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/">Back to language landing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <aside class="hero-panel panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Working Assumption</p>
        <h2>Build habits, not just installations.</h2>
        <p class="subtle">
          The guidebook is organized for researchers who need a stable daily workflow, not a one-time setup checklist.
        </p>
        {% if updates.latest %}
          <div class="update-chip">
            <span>{{ updates.latest.date }}</span>
            <a href="{{ updates.latest.url }}">{{ updates.latest.title }}</a>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-search wrap">
    {% set searchTitle = "Search the English guidebook" %}
    {% include "components/search-panel.njk" %}
  </section>

  <section class="editorial-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Category Map</p>
        <h2>Choose the part of the workflow you need next.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        {% for section in navigation.sections %}
          <a class="feature-card panel" href="{{ section.url.en }}">
            <p class="card-kicker">{{ section.kicker.en }}</p>
            <h3>{{ section.title.en }}</h3>
            <p>{{ section.summary.en }}</p>
          </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
